      "text": "What Can State Hold",
      "level": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The useState Hook can be used to keep track of strings, numbers, booleans, arrays, objects, and any combination of these!",
      "html": "<p>The <code>useState</code> Hook can be used to keep track of strings, numbers, booleans, arrays, objects, and any combination of these!</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "We could create multiple state Hooks to track individual values.",
      "html": "<p>We could create multiple state Hooks to track individual values.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "javascript",
        "tryItLink": null,
        "syntaxHighlighting": [],
        "classList": [
          "w3-white",
